Grupo BTG Pactual, controlled by
the Brazilian billionaire  Andre Esteves , hired Adriano Lima Borges as head of the Latin American business except Brazil,
according to two people familiar with the matter.  Borges was a director of Itau BBA, the wholesale arm of
 Itau Unibanco Holding SA (ITUB4) , since August 2009. He was a managing
director of Merrill Lynch & Co. from May 2008 to June 2009 and a
senior banker at Credit Suisse Group AG in Brazil. Borges has
also worked for Lehman Brothers Holdings Inc.  Borges didnâ€™t respond to calls for comment. Officials at
